headline: Bluesky Digital Assets Announces ChessGold Inc. Major Milestone
summary: TORONTO, Oct. 03, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Bluesky Digital Assets Corp., (CSE: BTC) (OTCQB: BTCWF), ("Bluesky" or the "Corporation") is pleased to announce that Chess Gold is Now Available on Apple Store with Apple Pay Integration — Expanding Global Access to Premium Chess. ChessGold, the next-generation platform for chess enthusiasts worldwide, has hit a major growth phase with explosive user engagement and massive infrastructure upgrades. ChessGold is officially available on the Apple App Stor
